Sentencas: In the present study, the polarization characteristics of La0.6Sr0.4Co0.2Fe0.8O3 (LSCF) - Gd0.1Ce0.9O1.95 (GDC) composite cathodes with different volume ratios were investigated.
Titulo: Evaluation of La0.6Sr0.4Co0.2Fe0.8O3-Gd0.1Ce0.9O1.95 composite cathode with three dimensional microstructure reconstruction

Sentencas: Samples with volume ratios of 20:80, 30:70, 50:50, 70:30 and 100:0 vol % were tested.
Titulo: Evaluation of La0.6Sr0.4Co0.2Fe0.8O3-Gd0.1Ce0.9O1.95 composite cathode with three dimensional microstructure reconstruction

Sentencas: The electrochemical impedance spectroscopy tests and current voltage curve measurements were carried out for the current densities from 0 to 0.2 Acm-2 with an interval of 0.05 Acm(-2).
Titulo: Evaluation of La0.6Sr0.4Co0.2Fe0.8O3-Gd0.1Ce0.9O1.95 composite cathode with three dimensional microstructure reconstruction

Sentencas: The results showed that a volume ratio of LSCF:GDC = 30:70 composite cathode led to the lowest overpotential, and the overpotential increased in the order of 30:70, 50:50, 70:30, 100:0, 20:80 vol %.
Titulo: Evaluation of La0.6Sr0.4Co0.2Fe0.8O3-Gd0.1Ce0.9O1.95 composite cathode with three dimensional microstructure reconstruction

Sentencas: Three dimensional microstructures of composite cathodes were reconstructed and quantified by dual beam focused ion beam-scanning electron microscope (FIB-SEM).
Titulo: Evaluation of La0.6Sr0.4Co0.2Fe0.8O3-Gd0.1Ce0.9O1.95 composite cathode with three dimensional microstructure reconstruction

Sentencas: The results showed that neither LSCF surface area nor triple phase boundary (TPB) alone could explain the dependence of polarization characteristics on volume ratios.
Titulo: Evaluation of La0.6Sr0.4Co0.2Fe0.8O3-Gd0.1Ce0.9O1.95 composite cathode with three dimensional microstructure reconstruction

Sentencas: Current and electrochemical potential distributions were simulated by the Lattice Boltzmann method, in which both surface and TPB reactions were considered.
Titulo: Evaluation of La0.6Sr0.4Co0.2Fe0.8O3-Gd0.1Ce0.9O1.95 composite cathode with three dimensional microstructure reconstruction

Sentencas: Prediction considering both surface and TPB reactions could predict qualitatively the dependence of overpotentials on LSCF - GDC cathode composition.
Titulo: Evaluation of La0.6Sr0.4Co0.2Fe0.8O3-Gd0.1Ce0.9O1.95 composite cathode with three dimensional microstructure reconstruction
